snippet.title: Lawgivers II - Political Simulation Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Lawgivers II is an upcoming political and geopolitical sandbox game for PC, Android and iOS.

Grab the exclusive "Kickstarter" edition today!! https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/damidev/lawgivers-ii
Join our discord to propose new ideas and suggestions: https://discord.com/invite/kE7juYR
